title: Command & Conquer Red Alert 2 + Yuri's Revenge [Win10 Fixed]
description:
Game.exe and gamemd.exe are the executables for RA2 and Yuri's Revenge respectively.



To enable Gamespeed control:

Create shortcuts for both and add the command -speedcontrol
E.g. "D:GamesCnC Red Alert 2Ra2.exe" -speedcontrol



Has been tested and played on Windows 10 64-bit. If it doesn't work for you, try running the game as administrator (right click icon -> Run as admin).

More options can be modified in RA2.ini and Ra2md.ini.

This game package has been configured to run at 1280 x 720 resolution
